      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Please no. We really don't need a combinatoric blowup in the number of supported wallet options and setups. How about instead support having a public-only HD seed (and if none is provided generate one, who cares, you're just watching a few extra addresses that will never be used).",
